channel.title: [PI] Adding Customs - Need HELP Finding the INT's etc
channel.description: Currently using a [PI], and I need to add a Death Cape, and some Dungeoneering armour. My server is a 317. So can anyone help me find the INT's w/e for both items, and tell me where to put them/ How to use them :P Thanks

item.title: [PI] Adding Customs - Need HELP Finding the INT's etc
item.dc:creator: @mr_extremez mr extremez
item.description:
@mr_extremez wrote:

ints go in itemdef.java client sided just google death cape model + ints and convert the ints to pi after you add the ints and the model server sided add it to item.cfg and you should be done
